{"tid":1439050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護界實名聯署 重申5大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T00:27:35.000Z","uid":36494,"like":291,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"b719f607ee848ff82a16ce75505e2a2e67ebf963","tid":1439050,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110325316976046/posts/111060530235858?s=100000528866832&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110325316976046%2Fposts%2F111060530235858%3Fs%3D100000528866832%26sfns%3Dmo&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68swmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=d859972d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110325316976046/posts/111060530235858?s=100000528866832&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一眾醫療界專職人員，時刻以守護市民身心健康為己任，竭盡所能服務市民大眾。<br />\n<br />\n近兩個月來一次又一次因反送中而發生的大型遊行示威及集會，市民聲嘶力竭，甚至以死作諫，政府依然故我，充耳不聞。更以警隊作為棋子，一次次以濫暴及無理鎮壓回應市民。<br />\n<br />\n我們痛心疾首。<br />\n<br />\n我們現懇請醫療界各專業界別參與「醫療界登報實名聯署」，再一次以更具公信力之手法促請政府立即正面回應香港人之五大訴求，以及撤銷註冊護士陳永琪日前參與人道救援時遭受的一切政治檢控。<br />\n<br />\n有意參與登報實名聯署之人士，請填妥表格，我們會先核對相關專業之名冊內的姓名及註冊編號。待人數足夠後便會公布眾籌事宜以支持登報之費用。執業會計師將會跟進一切相關帳目。如眾籌數目超過預期，扣除登報所需款項後，餘額將會捐至「立場新聞」及 「星火同盟抗爭支援」。<br />\n<br />\n我們 無畏站在公義的一方；<br />\n我們 無懼把真實姓名展露於人前。<br />\n<br />\n聯署表格：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/VG15gzxeRcrJAjMUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FVG15gzxeRcrJAjMUA&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68swmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=929cc910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/VG15gzxeRcrJAjMUA</a><br />\n各專業界別之名冊：<a href=\"https://tiny.cc/reglist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2Freglist&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68swmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=6245154e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tiny.cc/reglist</a><br />\n<br />\n請讚好/追蹤此專頁，日後聯署人數更新以及眾籌詳情將在此發佈。<br />\n<br />\n聯署發起人<br />\n歐耀佳 醫生 Dr AU Yiu Kai<br />\n陳偉雄 註冊護士 RN CHAN Bernard Wai Hung<br />\n范子信 註冊護士 RN FAN Tsz Shun<br />\n劉凱文 註冊護士 RN LAU Hoi Man Michael Felix<br />\n梁婷欣 註冊護士 RN LEUNG Ting Yan <br />\n梁子恆 醫生 Dr LEUNG Tsz Hang"},{"pid":"608fd20a4c013020e56b947d69180134ad8eef63","tid":1439050,"uid":82829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"痴線架！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16728b9bfb24c8ad43694e246111eb01c62d7f14","tid":1439050,"uid":68382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed2b261c272b29c0e2dd1da6ec497b315dd388a","tid":1439050,"uid":173814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"實名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860c074c8eccb0919dfa8ccfbf1801a91fd7d320","tid":1439050,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba8a3dd052c086a29263ab9d9de0f8c29d9c300","tid":1439050,"uid":36494,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"截至 10/8 00:00<br />\n聯署人數約 4200人"},{"pid":"7e716758d06ad2bf25c08e554e076b76b33b0cc4","tid":1439050,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"快啲簽啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：已簽"},{"pid":"fa5afbed5bd33502da1093e423d20aba67429bf6","tid":1439050,"uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"非醫護手足<br />\n麻煩通知做醫護界的朋友入去簽<br />\n<br />\n除咗醫生護士<br />\n下列專業界別都可以去簽㗎<br />\n